            <div class='post' itemprop='text'>
              <p>Any updates or newer info on this ?</p>
<p>For whatever reason: I had a ‚Äústyled‚Äù html table in a report when I was on hosted, but now I am on self hosted and any style tags are sanitized/removed.</p>
<p>Maybe there is a setting somewhere I am not aware of turn off sanitization ?</p>
            </div>

